rates and limited opportunities to expand.</p> <p>While it sounds bad, it really isn't, as it demonstrates the predictability of VICI as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809899503/image_1809899503.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741774-vici-properties-higher-interest-rates-arent-the-only-reason-for-underperformance", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 19:13:10"}, {"id": "4741772", "title": "The End Of An Era: What Gelsinger's Departure Means For Intel", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Headquarters\" data-id=\"1831946092\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> 