oads/getty_images/2165911634/image_2165911634.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741645-cardinal-energy-11-percent-dividend-yield-investing-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 18:30:00"}, {"id": "4741773", "title": "Renaissance Or Prelude To Chaos? Crypto's Role In The Trump Era", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Making Money in the Meta verse\" data-id=\"1419599523\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1086px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The cryptocurrency world has long had a tendency to thrive on volatility, sentiment, and narratives of reinvention. Yet, the recent surge in crypto enthusiasm following Donald Trump\u2019s reelection represents what many have described as a unique moment even in this hyperactive</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741773-renaissance-or-prelude-to-chaos-crypto-role-in-trump-era", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 18:20:00"}, {"id": "4741761", "title": "The Trade Desk: A Potential Roku Merger Augments Market Penetration (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digital marketing concept, Businessman using laptop with Ads dashboard digital marketing strategy analysis for branding. online advertisement, ad on website and social media. SEO. SMM.\" data-id=\"2098359215\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2098359215/image_2098359215.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024